Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Kingman Brewster
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407dtv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 May 1977
Kingman Brewster leaves Yale to take up appointment as UK ambassador. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. Programme recording incomplete. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less